Introducing the Fasthouse Off-Road Seeker Jacket. This rugged jacket is designed to handle whatever the trail throws at you. It's equipped with zip-off sleeves that neatly tuck away into a convenient back pocket, giving you versatile style and functionality. 

Made to endure the elements, the Seeker jacket boasts a DWR (Durable Water-Repellent) coating to keep you dry during unexpected showers. Stay cool and comfortable while tearing up the trails with the built-in back vent, allowing for optimal airflow. The jacket also sports reinforced key areas prone to abrasion, ensuring long-lasting durability, even in the roughest terrain.

Body (HTML):
Based directly off the proven Grindhouse pant, the Speed/Style version offers a super comfortable and lightweight body resulting in an ultra-high-performance pant. By using the best-fitting, flexible, highest wear-resistant sublimated stretch panels we could find and putting them just in the right spot we ended up with one of the comfiest pair of riding pants we have ever ridden in.

 Features:

  • 600 Denier Poly main panel construction.
  • 2 way stretch knee and rear yoke panels.
  • Lightweight, breathable and snag resistant thigh and calf panels.
  • High strength Nylon thread double and triple stitched seams.
  • High heat and abrasion resistant Full Grain Leather inner knee panels.
  • Punched Poly front panel allows just the right amount of venting.
  • Long-lasting silk-screened thigh panel graphic.
  • 4 way stretch dyed shin panels.
  • Durable and pliable TPR knee embellishments.
  • Silky soft Tricot 3/4 length knee brace optimised lining.
  • Patterned and fit for every style of rider.

Fit, function, simplicity. This pant skips all the over-engineered razzle-dazzle of today's current batch of riding pants and goes straight to the tried and true features that have been time-proven and we know works. With that as the core focus of everything Fasthouse produces, our first entry into the pant market is a workhorse.

Durable enough for countless weekends with your friends in the desert or at the track, yet high-performance enough to line up at Supercross.

Durable enough for countless weekends with your friends in the desert or at the track, yet high-performance enough to line up at Supercross.

 Features:

  • 600 Denier poly main panel construction.
  • 2 way stretch knee and rear yoke panels.
  • Lightweight, breathable and snag resistant thigh and calf panels.
  • High strength nylon thread double and triple stitched seams.
  • High heat and abrasion resistant Full Grain Leather inner knee panels.
  • Punched poly front panel allows just the right amount of venting.
  • Durable and pliable TPR thigh and knee embellishments.
  • Silky soft Tricot 3/4 length knee brace optimised lining.
  • Patterned and fit for every style of rider.

With that as the core focus of everything Fasthouse produces, our first entry into the pant market is a workhorse.

Durable enough for countless weekends with your friends in the desert or at the track, yet high-performance enough to line up at Supercross.

 Features:

  • 600 Denier Poly main panel construction.
  • 2 way stretch knee and rear yoke panels.
  • Lightweight, breathable and snag resistant thigh and calf panels.
  • High strength Nylon thread double and triple stitched seams.
  • High heat and abrasion resistant Full Grain Leather inner knee panels.
  • Punched Poly front panel allows just the right amount of venting.
  • Durable thigh screen prints and TPR knee embellishments.
  • Silky soft Tricot 3/4 length knee brace optimised lining.
  • Patterned and fit for every style of rider.

The Air Cooled "A/C" ELROD Series is our most breathable, top-of-the-line, feature-loaded racing gear kit! These latest "A/C" ELROD Jerseys, Pants and Gloves feature maximum ventilation, lighter materials, slimmer fit and reinforced stitching to ensure superior performance and improved comfort for every race and ride. Prefer less ventilation or racing/riding in colder weather? Check out our standard ELROD kit!

 Features: 

  • 4-Way stretch Cordura® offers unrestricted movement throughout pant.
  • Wide-hole mesh vented thigh panelling for maximum lower body airflow.
  • Perforated 450D front panel & back yoke panel for additional ventilation.
  • Solid 600D back thigh and saddle panel for superior abrasion resistance.
  • Ultralight mesh vented back calf & ankle panelling improves boot airflow.
  • Mini mesh front thigh & inner back yoke inserts. Interior silicone gripper.
  • Double & triple stitched seams reinforced with high strength nylon yarns.
  • Large high heat/abrasion resistant full grain leather inner knee panelling.
  • Durable yet pliable TPR embellishments on thighs, knees and back yoke.
  • Silky soft 3/4 length inner lining for comfort and knee brace optimization.
  • Front zipper closure with adjust ratchet strap & side waistband adjustors.
  • Removable / interchangeable front thigh patch. Back yoke TPR locker tab.
  • Slim athletic racing fit: this is our slimmest and tightest fitting pant style.
  • 55% Polyester/38% Nylon/7% Spandex. Fully dyed for long lasting colour.

Our Everywhere Chamois Liner.

Liner Features:

  • 87% Polyester, 13% Spandex material.
  • Ultrathin breathable stretch mesh fabric.
  • Jacquard Fasthouse checker elastic waistband.
  • Premium chamois pad with stamped FH logo.
  • Dye sublimated black & grey stripe side panels.
  • Microdot silicone grip on lower thigh bands.
  • 8.5" inseam length, stretch form fit.

Pad Features:

  • Ergonomically designed for anatomical body contouring. 
  • High density five layer foam structure for improved comfort.
  • Anti-bacterial, mildew resistant moisture wicking materials.
  • Embedded anti-shock gel pockets for increased protection.
  • 5mm perforated holes on underside for superior ventilation.

Alloy Stripe Long Sleeve Jersey Black L
Body (HTML):
New Fit. Race Ready.

Alloy is our top-of-the-line, feature-loaded long sleeve BIKE jersey. We've upgraded this jersey with some cool new touches to make your rides more comfortable and improve your performance. Now available in a variety of colours, this jersey looks great however you mix-and-match it. 

 Features: 

  • FastDri fabric wicks moisture away from the body.
  • Built-in zipper pocket with reflective reinforcement tabs.
  • Fully dyed fabrics to ensure true long lasting colour.
  • V-cut stretch collar to reduce pressure against neck.
  • High quality silk screened graphic on front chest & left sleeve.
  • Reflective stretch transfer graphic on right sleeve.
  • Ultrathin stretch transfer neck label for improved comfort.
  • Mesh vented under arms / wrist & back for increased cooling.
  • Slight drop tail on pack panel for full coverage while riding.
  • Overlocked stitching for improved durability.
  • 94% Polyester, 6% Spandex.
  • Athletic jersey fit.

New Fit. Race Ready.

Alloy is our top-of-the-line, feature-loaded long sleeve BIKE jersey. We've upgraded this jersey with some cool new touches to make your rides more comfortable and improve your performance. Now available in a variety of colours, this jersey looks great however you mix-and-match it.

  • Overlocked stitching for improved durability.

  • Thick stripe pattern on back panel.
  • 94% Polyester, 6% Spandex.
  • Athletic jersey fit.

Introducing the new Fasthouse "Speed Star" 22oz Water Bottle, developed using Purist technology that shields the inside of the bottle from any bad taste, mould or staining. As pure as drinking from a glass, but with all the advantages of a flexible bottle. Nothing sticks, so your bottle stays clean and your water always tastes pure. This bottle includes a wide translucent strip, so you know exactly how much water remains.

Our water bottle also features the most advanced screw cap on the market; the Watergate. With a simple hands-free open and close heart valve, there's no turning required to access your water. The cap doesn’t require opening or closing, a simple squeeze is all you need to open the heart valve and take a drink—no need to fumble with opening or closing a bottle mid-ride. This heart valve delivers a high rate of flow with a 100% leak proof design. The cap also locks down for transport or mixing powdered drinks, and the rubber over-mould grip helps for easy cap removal.

This bottle is made with easy-to-squeeze LDPE material and features an amorphous silicon dioxide coating that's infused into the inner-wall of the bottle. It uses BPA-Free plastic, is made from 100% FDA food-grade materials and is printed with non-solvent base (UV Cured), CPSC-approved ink and materials.
